data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Irving! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath gem on a corner lot in a cul-de-sac offers move-in-ready comfort. Enjoy tile floors, granite countertops, and an open kitchen-living area. Also has space for an office or flex room, 2-car garage, and a fantastic covered deck for outdoor living. This home is a perfect blend of style and convenience, in the heart of the metroplex and a about 10 minutes from DFW International Airport. Don't miss out—schedule your viewing today!
